CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 24, reads: "Sponsors - The charming sextette, Lucille Walker, Ethel Slaughter, Virginia Peterson, Barbara Griffin, Louise Harris and Valdoras Love, are sponsors of 'Club Cosmopolitan' which will be opened Friday Oct. 19. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Lucille Walker, Ethel Slaughter, Virginia Peterson, Barbara Griffin, Louise Harris, and Valdoras Love, posed in Coca-Cola booth, seen from above
